{"tid":30882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該想走既人諗下係為咩而過黎","createTime":"2016-12-09T10:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T12:54:42.000Z","uid":22323,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a66a6fb9bda70a9d16fb0d9f38efbc4605c69bcd","tid":30882,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T10:58:42.000Z","msg":"如果係因為熱潮既話<br />\n而家過左啦，走把啦<br />\n唔係既話，唔該你地到底反思下自己點解要離開<br />\n諗下點解要過黎？<br />\n過到黎開個新壇，admin本身無管理論壇既經驗<br />\n你地唔會諗住一過到黎就咩都會比高登果邊好啊話？<br />\n問心果句，呢邊admin有無盡力做，我相信有心人都看在眼內<br />\n刪po事件，emoji都好，次次都見到admin迅速回應<br />\n再對比下果邊呢？唔係因為發現開始無人上，佢會理你整個新既手機版？<br />\n麻煩你地諗下初衷<br />\n仲有，係屌呢邊5化既同時，你又有無為此而盡力？"},{"pid":"28c25da0ea6f6197bb18acec5d73864c9c9fe8b3","tid":30882,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:05:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"742c676a122f0e66750afba63a0b30be8184bb3f","tid":30882,"uid":43146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:05:46.000Z","msg":"block緊啲5p 仔，成班垃圾奶都未戒仲逗緊零用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d436b3bfc74cc9d78ff03964bac0565deac0be77","tid":30882,"uid":49685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ea3b61de702b235ee8b82602c041c3ac8c9c25","tid":30882,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:07:14.000Z","msg":"過黎咪因為ios無好app上hkg囉<br />\n講咁多佛計托咩"},{"pid":"5fd58216cf1e25e4f2aa364ddb4ca6369dbb50d1","tid":30882,"uid":22323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>block緊啲5p 仔，成班垃圾奶都未戒仲逗緊零用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好淨係block佢地<br />\n仲要見一個屌瑋個<br />\n屌到佢地化<br />\n屌到佢地怕"},{"pid":"5bef7ac49571185c897f0c208bfad1f0efc1c46a","tid":30882,"uid":50533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11